Repost from @thetravelmom

Mālama means to take care of, tend, attend, care for, preserve, protect. Watch this great video explaining what it means for the Islands of Hawaii and how YOU can help. This is such an important concept for all of us, no matter where we live. Feel free to share it so hopefully we can inspire others. @gohawaii @hawaiianairlines @hiltonhawaiianvillage @hiltonhotels @oahuvb @gunstockranch @hawaiinewsnow
